                <note rend="inline" type="source">561.35E1A/105: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-10-02T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 2, 1937—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>407. Your 619, September 28, 6 p.m. There is no objection to inclusion of an
                    Agenda item concerning American Sugar Act for the stated purposes.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
